(418, 'product_main_description', '<p>Integrating marketing plan functionality into Dash SaaS represents a significant advancement in campaign management, enabling businesses to orchestrate, execute, and analyze marketing initiatives seamlessly within a single platform. By centralizing key marketing processes, Dash SaaS empowers teams to optimize their strategies, streamline workflows, and drive greater ROI from their marketing efforts.</p>', 'MarketingPlan', '2024-12-07 09:20:13', '2024-12-07 09:20:13'),
