(556, 'product_main_description', '<p>To start receiving reminders, simply enable the reminder button from the system settings. Once activated, you\'ll receive timely alerts for all your scheduled reminders across your selected sources. This feature ensures that you never miss an important event or deadline, helping you stay productive and on top of your tasks.</p>', 'Reminder', '2024-12-07 09:22:08', '2024-12-07 09:22:08'),
