(694, 'product_main_description', '<p>Our Planning Module streamlines project management with comprehensive Challenge and Charter functionalities. Challenges provide a structured framework for project goals and timelines, while Charters define the specific roles, responsibilities, and tasks. The system ensures seamless collaboration and efficient tracking of project progress. With our setup, managing complex projects becomes intuitive and effective.\n        </p>', 'Planning', '2024-12-07 10:19:30', '2024-12-07 10:19:30'),
